<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
      <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Your CPT Worksheet</h2>

      <p>Hello <%= @user.email %>,</p>

      <p>Please find your <strong><%= @worksheet_type %></strong> worksheet attached to this email.</p>

      <p><strong>Worksheet:</strong> <%= @worksheet.title %></p>

      <p>The PDF file is attached to this email and can be viewed, printed, or saved for your records.</p>

      <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 20px 0;">

      <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
        This email was sent from CPT with Ross. If you did not request this worksheet,
        please disregard this email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
